Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:06.59,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}自分らしさってなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.35,0:01:09.84,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}「人とは違う」で差をつけろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.08,0:01:12.32,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}コンビニの雑誌コーナー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:15.71,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}表紙にふとして書いてあった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:18.05,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}自分らしさってなんだ　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:21.07,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}子供の頃は気にもせず
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:24.03,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}気に入らなければ怒って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:26.95,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}好きなものを好きだと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:30.12,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}僕らは変わってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:32.99,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}守りたいものが変わってゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:35.74,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}理解されない宝物から
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:38.48,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}理解されるための建前へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:44.01,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}大人になるほど　後悔する生き物になる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:46.63,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}でもね　それでもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:50.96,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}見えるものがあるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:58.05,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}だから僕は僕らしく　そして君は君らしくって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:04.04,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}初めから　探すようなものではないんだと思うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:09.31,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}僕は君じゃないし　君も僕じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:12.18,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}すれ違う　手をつなぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:16.79,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}そこには愛だって生まれる　そういうもんさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:20.69,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}自分らしさってなんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:26.81,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}変えられない　大切があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:30.56,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}変わりゆく生活が　正しい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:06.59,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}何为个性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.35,0:01:09.84,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}独特的风格  会让你无与伦比
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.08,0:01:12.32,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}扉页题着如此文字的书籍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:15.71,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}静躺在路边小店的角落里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:18.05,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}何为个性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:21.07,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}懵懂的我不愿思考这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:24.03,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}若是不合心意 便大发雷霆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:26.95,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}若是合了心意 便坦率欢喜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:30.12,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}成长的脚步不会停歇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:32.99,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}珍视的事物也随之改变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:35.74,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}舍弃手中晦涩的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:38.48,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}戴上世人认同的假面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:44.01,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}越长大 越要体味苦涩的悔意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:46.63,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}没关系 即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:50.96,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}有些东西 只有成熟后才能看清
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:58.05,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}你和我 都有着独一无二的个性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:04.04,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}一开始 就无需费尽心思地追寻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:09.31,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}我就是我 你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:12.18,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}擦肩而过 牵手结缘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:16.79,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}爱的诞生 就是如此简单
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:20.69,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}何为个性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:26.81,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}正因有着不变的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:30.56,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}瞬息万变的生活 才是个性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.21,0:21:13.66,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You held out a small hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:19.55,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Smiling like to you it was so natural
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.72,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It may have no meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:30.49,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}but it is something I cannot do
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:36.56,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You touched my hand without thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:40.35,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}but it was nice for me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:48.67,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}All the time we believed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.79,0:21:54.15,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}that the world was in our hands
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:57.05,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}We were wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:22:05.12,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}maybe it wasn't 'cause \Nyou're holding my hand now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:10.74,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}At every moment
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:16.28,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:21.61,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}I can believe, I can believe
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:26.79,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}When I'm holding your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:34.16,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.21,0:21:13.66,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}你伸出的手稚气未脱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:19.55,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}宛若唇边浅浅的笑涡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.72,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}它于无意中动人心魄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:30.49,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}无缘的我却徒添寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:36.56,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}你漫不经心地触碰我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:40.35,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}殊不知暖流浸满我的心头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:48.67,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}回首昔日  我们坚信不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.79,0:21:54.15,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}手中所握  便是一树菩提
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:57.05,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}阴差阳错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:22:05.12,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}这一刻  世界也融化于你双手的温热
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:10.74,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}无时无刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:16.28,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}不论何处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:21.61,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}我的信仰  坚守不渝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:26.79,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}请让我贪恋你手心的温度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:34.16,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}手心的温度
